============

Test Sendmail
$: echo &quot;Hello there&quot; | /usr/sbin/sendmail example@gmail.com


Show the queue
$: sendmail -bp
/var/spool/mqueue is empty
		Total requests: 0


Flush the queue
$: sendmail -q </pre></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="footer">Powered by <a href="http://www.sinatrarb.com/">Sinatra</a>,
